<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .about-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .restaurant-image {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-content {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-section">
        <img src="../restaurant.jpeg" alt="Restaurant Image" class="restaurant-image">
        <div class="about-content">
            <p>Welcome to our website, where culinary excellence meets a delightful dining experience. Our passion for creating memorable meals is reflected in every dish we serve.</p>
            <p> we strive to provide an inviting atmosphere where friends and family can gather to savor exceptional flavors. Join us on a culinary journey that celebrates the art of food and the joy of sharing it with others.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
    &copy; 2023. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>
</body>
</html>
